1
00:00:31,066 --> 00:00:32,066
Waterfall!

2
00:00:32,133 --> 00:00:33,133
Had fun?

3
00:00:35,133 --> 00:00:36,500
Where has Kriss sis gone again?

4
00:00:37,066 --> 00:00:38,966
Or has she gone to fine another guy?

5
00:00:40,233 --> 00:00:41,233
Probably.

6
00:00:41,266 --> 00:00:44,266
Okay, everyone.
You guys should get some rest.

7
00:00:44,766 --> 00:00:45,766
- Yes.
- Yes.

8
00:00:45,933 --> 00:00:47,000
Imma take my leave.

9
00:00:47,333 --> 00:00:49,413
If you got any problems,
feel free to give me a call.

10
00:00:49,766 --> 00:00:50,800
Okay, bro.

11
00:00:51,466 --> 00:00:53,233
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

12
00:00:53,233 --> 00:00:54,500
- See you.
- See you.

13
00:00:55,500 --> 00:00:57,166
So damn tired.

14
00:00:57,533 --> 00:00:59,199
Hey, boys.

15
00:00:59,199 --> 00:01:02,166
Where have you been?
Why did you come back this late?

16
00:01:02,300 --> 00:01:08,500
We went to waterfall. We're so tired
and starving. Do you have anything for us?

17
00:01:08,833 --> 00:01:10,933
Alright.

18
00:01:10,933 --> 00:01:12,000
Me too.

19
00:01:14,033 --> 00:01:16,366
I'll get right to it.

20
00:01:16,433 --> 00:01:17,433
Please hurry, sis.

21
00:01:17,699 --> 00:01:19,333
Okay.

22
00:01:20,400 --> 00:01:23,466
We should take a shower first
and then we eat.

23
00:01:23,466 --> 00:01:24,900
We're going, sis. Bye.

24
00:01:42,266 --> 00:01:43,266
Chok.

25
00:01:43,300 --> 00:01:46,666
Deliver me two crates of honey right now.

26
00:01:46,866 --> 00:01:48,199
Right now.

27
00:01:48,800 --> 00:01:50,033
Okay.
